  "title": "Restaurant Cook – Karnataka / Bangalore Cuisine",
  "description": "<h3>Job Description</h3><p>We are an Indian bar specialising in authentic Karnataka (Bangalore-style) bar bites and small plates. We are looking for a Restaurant Cook with hands-on experience in Bangalore food culture, traditional flavours, and popular Karnataka bar snacks.</p><p>The role focuses on accurate preparation of regional dishes, maintaining consistency during service, and supporting daily kitchen operations in a fast-paced bar environment.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Prepare and cook regional Karnataka dishes according to menu standards</p></li><li><p>Apply correct Karnataka spice blends and masalas to maintain authentic flavours</p></li><li><p>Cook Bangalore-style bar snacks efficiently during peak service hours</p></li><li><p>Assist with daily kitchen operations, including food preparation and service support</p></li><li><p>Ensure food quality, portion control, and consistency</p></li><li><p>Maintain kitchen cleanliness, hygiene, and food safety standards</p></li><li><p>Follow standard operating procedures and comply with health regulations</p></li><li><p>Work collaboratively with kitchen team members to ensure smooth workflow</p></li></ul><h3>Job Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Minimum 2–3 years of relevant cooking experience, preferably in Karnataka / Bangalore cuisine</p></li><li><p>Hands-on experience preparing Bangalore-style food (not limited to general Indian cuisine)</p></li><li><p>Familiarity with Bangalore food culture, street food, and bar-style dishes</p></li><li><p>Ability to work efficiently in a fast-paced kitchen environment</p></li><li><p>Willingness to follow instructions and work under supervision</p></li><li><p>Team player with a positive attitude and strong work ethic</p></li></ul>",
